{"tid":1568252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[借刀]藍絲圍商場應該要好好利用，而唔係阻止佢地同佢對撼","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:05:31.000Z","uid":59887,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab438c66655cf9b70c268d1fa9cc1ea3230f97c5","tid":1568252,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"見唔見淘大班商舖驚撚到落哂閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有幾可見到商場唱榮光果陣會落閘封舖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班業主唔係蠢嘅 邊班先真正搞事佢地有眼見<br />\n佢地要圍？圍囉<br />\n佢地叫撐警？叫囉<br />\n你落去同佢衝突就會被寫成係示威者衝擊商場搞到無生意<br />\n人地都幫我地做埋一份，點解唔好好利用 又慳水又慳力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用文宣好好煲大佢仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999f90ca0109e9c769535a169faa9a62d5f7f88e","tid":1568252,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:00:20.000Z","msg":"藍絲口講清潔，唱國歌，實質搶嘢！打人發洩！"},{"pid":"2a22b73955208d70a2766286b957d5e73815b2d7","tid":1568252,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"要藍絲幫手助攻先係良方<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ae8412c654b8b1d950657a40c6eff7cb16194d","tid":1568252,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c626610dafaec67a9307c4e6bce662478c2c7b6b","tid":1568252,"uid":12768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de208b93cc9959d7967378c57bb6a805753c23d8","tid":1568252,"uid":59887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"無視所有藍絲愛國活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23ac4a7e88a9d620a8af181314eb45e79e59a01","tid":1568252,"uid":201374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"啲藍絲都識見到人多就縮啦<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺唱榮光集會嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺組團修牆嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n知唔知點解佢哋唔喺大遊行嘅時候吹雞搞事?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為佢哋知自己吹雞唔夠人會俾人打返轉頭啊</span></span><br />\n連藍絲都識敵進我退,去淘大嗰班就唔識,明知冇PLAN好一定唔撚夠人都照衝,重蠢過藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔使再問遊行有警察係咪唔去<br />\n屌你咩每次遊行宣傳咗幾耐?有PLAN定有事前計劃咪會夠人囉,夠人咪去囉<br />\n朝早宣佈下晝有遊行,然後現場有幾百隻狗等你,你都唔撚去啦<br />\nbe water唔代表啲water識瞬間移動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日去淘大嗰班&quot;手足&quot;,同825嗰隻藍衫的士佬一樣咁戇鳩</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUkUVtU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUkUVtU.gif&h=8cdf3b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係以為藍絲企定定俾你打,以為自己可以一打十咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82261e6f9f6f1d80f15cf3566dc67e68974a073a","tid":1568252,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"顯示藍黃高下之別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8269548dea970a0534588035046c0546c8d386b","tid":1568252,"uid":169391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"推推推！冷處理佢地，唔好去同佢地對撼。到佢地7左，就文宣煲大佢，等其他藍絲覺得恥與為伍"}]}